    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Upon receiving the 6th level of this Class Mod, you unlock the most powerful transformation of all. By combining your chakra and the Twisted Chakra of the Sealed Beast, you can multiply its potency exponentially, though the risk of using it is great.</p><p><strong>Gaining Baryon Mode</strong> is completely <strong>DM and game dependent</strong>. As there is no direct path to attaining it, the decision for when or if this portion of the Class Mod is used is wholly in the hands of the <strong>DM</strong> and/or <strong>players</strong> as they build the world.</p>",
